texts.html: 30 de April de 201527 de May de 2015 by Cátia

So April is coming to an end and May is about to start. This means that in the next month more amazing books are going to bo released. Maybe the continuation of a series comes out or even a stand alone that you want to read. So, these are some of the books that are going to be released May. If you want more information about the book click on its cover. It will take to the Goodreads page.

Ooh I can’t wait to read A Court of Thorns and Roses! Wow, Sarah J. Maas must be a really quick writer if she can get two books out in a year!
I’m also really excited for The Heir. I just finished the Selection trilogy (well, series… And I guess I didn’t finish it because there is a new book coming out…) I wonder how that will all work? From what I’ve gathered it is one of the future princess and it’s just a selection for her?
